Name: LogoCutDepth
Comments: How deep the logo is cut into the badge.

Name: LogoCutOffset

Name: FlareHeight
Comments: How tall the rear notch is cut to make way for the bottom right flare in the powerwall port area.

Name: FrontFaceDepth
Comments: How deep the face goes before the loft starts

Name: FaceCornerRadius
